(NULL,'IRDAI.PR.IP.204','Is appropriate immutable backup and Failover/Resilient components available for critical hardware?','Is appropriate immutable backup and Failover/Resilient components available for critical hardware?','IRDAI CSF Compliance','technical','detective','annual',TRUE),
(NULL,'IRDAI.PR.IP.205','Is it ensured that only software applications or operating systems currently supported by the software''s vendor are adde','Is it ensured that only software applications or operating systems currently supported by the software''s vendor are added to the organization''s authorized software inventory? Unsupported software should be tagged as','IRDAI CSF Compliance','technical','detective','annual',TRUE),
(NULL,'IRDAI.PR.IP.206','Is it ensured that the software inventory system should be tied into the hardware asset inventory so all devices and ass','Is it ensured that the software inventory system should be tied into the hardware asset inventory so all devices and associated software are tracked from a single location?','IRDAI CSF Compliance','technical','detective','annual',TRUE),
(NULL,'IRDAI.PR.IP.207','Is the use of remote access software restricted?','Is the use of remote access software restricted?','IRDAI CSF Compliance','technical','detective','annual',TRUE),
(NULL,'IRDAI.PR.IP.208','Is there documentation describing data, programs, hardware, and system requirements?','Is there documentation describing data, programs, hardware, and system requirements?','IRDAI CSF Compliance','technical','detective','annual',TRUE),
(NULL,'IRDAI.PR.IP.209','Are policies and procedures being used to protect critical information at different layers of security?','Are policies and procedures being used to protect critical information at different layers of security?','IRDAI CSF Compliance','technical','detective','annual',TRUE),
(NULL,'IRDAI.PR.MA.210','Is there a process to determine after how many days of identification, patches would be fixed?','Is there a process to determine after how many days of identification, patches would be fixed?','IRDAI CSF Compliance','technical','detective','annual',TRUE),
(NULL,'IRDAI.PR.MA.211','Are remote maintenance of organizational assets approved, logged, and performed in a manner that prevents unauthorized a','Are remote maintenance of organizational assets approved, logged, and performed in a manner that prevents unauthorized access?','IRDAI CSF Compliance','technical','detective','annual',TRUE),
(NULL,'IRDAI.PR.MA.212','Are Defined parameters  taken for prioritizing the patches need to be installed?','Are Defined parameters  taken for prioritizing the patches need to be installed?','IRDAI CSF Compliance','technical','detective','annual',TRUE),
(NULL,'IRDAI.PR.MA.213','Are maintenance and repair of organizational assets logged whenever performed, with approved and controlled tools?','Are maintenance and repair of organizational assets logged whenever performed, with approved and controlled tools?','IRDAI CSF Compliance','technical','detective','annual',TRUE),
(NULL,'IRDAI.PR.MA.214','Is there a process to deploy critical patches in a test environment?','Is there a process to deploy critical patches in a test environment?','IRDAI CSF Compliance','technical','detective','annual',TRUE),
(NULL,'IRDAI.PR.MA.215','Are the approved patch management policy have been implemented?','Are the approved patch management policy have been implemented?','IRDAI CSF Compliance','technical','detective','annual',TRUE),
(NULL,'IRDAI.PR.MA.216','Have parameters been defined for classifying patches?','Have parameters been defined for classifying patches?','IRDAI CSF Compliance','technical','detective','annual',TRUE),
(NULL,'IRDAI.PR.PT.217','Are adequate measures taken to isolate and secure the perimeter and connectivity of the servers running monetary transac','Are adequate measures taken to isolate and secure the perimeter and connectivity of the servers running monetary transactions applications/process?','IRDAI CSF Compliance','technical','detective','annual',TRUE),
(NULL,'IRDAI.PR.PT.218','Does the organization Continuously monitor the release of patches by various vendors / OEMs, advisories issued by CERT-i','Does the organization Continuously monitor the release of patches by various vendors / OEMs, advisories issued by CERT-in and other similar agencies and expeditiously apply the security patches as per the patch management policy?','IRDAI CSF Compliance','technical','detective','annual',TRUE),
(NULL,'IRDAI.PR.PT.219','Has the organization deployed controls like host / network / application based IDS systems, customized kernels for Linux','Has the organization deployed controls like host / network / application based IDS systems, customized kernels for Linux, anti- virus and anti-malware software','IRDAI CSF Compliance','technical','detective','annual',TRUE),
(NULL,'IRDAI.PR.PT.220','Has the organization documented and implemented secure mail and messaging systems that include measures to prevent email','Has the organization documented and implemented secure mail and messaging systems that include measures to prevent email spoofing, identical mail domains, protection of attachments, malicious links etc.?','IRDAI CSF Compliance','technical','detective','annual',TRUE),
(NULL,'IRDAI.PR.PT.221','Has the organization established baseline standards to facilitate consistent application of security configurations to o','Has the organization established baseline standards to facilitate consistent application of security configurations to operating systems, databases, network devices and enterprise mobile devices within their IT environment? Are LAN and wireless networks secured within organizations premises by deploying proper controls?','IRDAI CSF Compliance','technical','detective','annual',TRUE),
(NULL,'IRDAI.PR.PT.222','Has the organization implemented mechanism to control installation of software/applications on end- user PCs, laptops, w','Has the organization implemented mechanism to control installation of software/applications on end- user PCs, laptops, workstations, servers, mobile devices, etc. and mechanism to block /prevent and identify installation and running of unauthorised','IRDAI CSF Compliance','technical','detective','annual',TRUE),
(NULL,'IRDAI.PR.PT.223','Has the organization installed network security devices, such as firewalls, proxy servers, intrusion detection and preve','Has the organization installed network security devices, such as firewalls, proxy servers, intrusion detection and prevention systems (IDS) to protect their IT infrastructure which is exposed to the internet, from security exposures originating from internal and external sources?','IRDAI CSF Compliance','technical','detective','annual',TRUE),
(NULL,'IRDAI.RC.CO.224','Are recovery activities communicated to internal and external stakeholders as well as executive and management team?','Are recovery activities communicated to internal and external stakeholders as well as executive and management team?','IRDAI CSF Compliance','technical','detective','annual',TRUE),
(NULL,'IRDAI.RC.IM.225','Are recovery strategies updated periodically?','Are recovery strategies updated periodically?','IRDAI CSF Compliance','technical','detective','annual',TRUE),
(NULL,'IRDAI.RC.IM.226','Does recovery plans incorporate lessons learned?','Does recovery plans incorporate lessons learned?','IRDAI CSF Compliance','technical','detective','annual',TRUE),
(NULL,'IRDAI.RC.RP.227','Is recovery plan executed during or after a cybersecurity incident?','Is recovery plan executed during or after a cybersecurity incident?','IRDAI CSF Compliance','technical','detective','annual',TRUE),
(NULL,'IRDAI.RS.AN.228','Are processes established to receive, analyse and respond to vulnerabilities disclosed to the organization from internal','Are processes established to receive, analyse and respond to vulnerabilities disclosed to the organization from internal and external sources? (e.g. internal testing, security bulletins, or security researchers)','IRDAI CSF Compliance','technical','detective','annual',TRUE),
(NULL,'IRDAI.RS.AN.229','Does the organisation have a process to ensure that impact of an incident analysed?','Does the organisation have a process to ensure that impact of an incident analysed?','IRDAI CSF Compliance','technical','detective','annual',TRUE),
(NULL,'IRDAI.RS.AN.230','Does the organisation have a process to ensure that Notifications from detection systems are investigated ?','Does the organisation have a process to ensure that Notifications from detection systems are investigated ?','IRDAI CSF Compliance','technical','detective','annual',TRUE),
(NULL,'IRDAI.RS.AN.231','Does the organisation have a process to ensure that forensics are performed?','Does the organisation have a process to ensure that forensics are performed?','IRDAI CSF Compliance','technical','detective','annual',TRUE),
(NULL,'IRDAI.RS.CO.232','Are all the cyber attacks related incidents captured and logged?','Are all the cyber attacks related incidents captured and logged?','IRDAI CSF Compliance','technical','detective','annual',TRUE),
(NULL,'IRDAI.RS.CO.233','Are the cyber related incident reported to higher authority on periodic basis?','Are the cyber related incident reported to higher authority on periodic basis?','IRDAI CSF Compliance','technical','detective','annual',TRUE),
(NULL,'IRDAI.RS.CO.234','Are cyber incidents reported to CERT-In within 6 hours of noticing or being brought to notice about such incidents?','Are cyber incidents reported to CERT-In within 6 hours of noticing or being brought to notice about such incidents?','IRDAI CSF Compliance','technical','detective','annual',TRUE),
(NULL,'IRDAI.RS.CO.235','Are third parties contractually required to protect the information that is shared with them as part of an incident?','Are third parties contractually required to protect the information that is shared with them as part of an incident?','IRDAI CSF Compliance','technical','detective','annual',TRUE),
(NULL,'IRDAI.RS.CO.236','Are Contact details of Ministries, stakeholders, vendors and agencies like NCIIPC & CERT-In for incident resolutions up ','Are Contact details of Ministries, stakeholders, vendors and agencies like NCIIPC & CERT-In for incident resolutions up to date and documented?','IRDAI CSF Compliance','technical','detective','annual',TRUE),
(NULL,'IRDAI.RS.CO.237','Are the timelines prescribed for reporting incidents to external organizations including IRDAI, CERT-In strictly adhered','Are the timelines prescribed for reporting incidents to external organizations including IRDAI, CERT-In strictly adhered to?','IRDAI CSF Compliance','technical','detective','annual',TRUE),
