(NULL,'IRDAI.RS.RP.248','Does the organisation Ensure that all backups have at least one backup destination that is not continuously addressable ','Does the organisation Ensure that all backups have at least one backup destination that is not continuously addressable through operating system calls / offline backup ?','IRDAI CSF Compliance','technical','detective','annual',TRUE),
(NULL,'IRDAI.RS.RP.249','Does the organisation Ensure that all of the organization''s key / critical systems are backed up as a complete system, t','Does the organisation Ensure that all of the organization''s key / critical systems are backed up as a complete system, through processes such as imaging, to enable the quick recovery of an entire system.','IRDAI CSF Compliance','technical','detective','annual',TRUE),
