(NULL,'IRDAI.WFRL.279','Are controls in place to identify unauthorized access, malicious code execution, suspicious activities or behaviour, cre','Are controls in place to identify unauthorized access, malicious code execution, suspicious activities or behaviour, credential theft, presence of advance persistent threats like remote access toolkits and such cyber','IRDAI CSF Compliance','technical','detective','annual',TRUE),
(NULL,'IRDAI.WFRL.280','Are email services secured to prevent spam, spoofed mails and malware filtering?','Are email services secured to prevent spam, spoofed mails and malware filtering?','IRDAI CSF Compliance','technical','detective','annual',TRUE),
