(NULL,'IRDAI.WFRL.292','In the case of disruption can IT support be accessed by investment application users through portal, help desk (phone) o','In the case of disruption can IT support be accessed by investment application users through portal, help desk (phone) or email or visit to office?','IRDAI CSF Compliance','technical','detective','annual',TRUE),
