(NULL,'IRDAI.WFRL.295','Is data restoration testing performed on periodic basis to ensure integrity of backups?','Is data restoration testing performed on periodic basis to ensure integrity of backups?','IRDAI CSF Compliance','technical','detective','annual',TRUE),
