(NULL,'IRDAI.WFRL.299','Are  applications accessible ONLY to authorised users through a secured VPN or VDI access?','Are  applications accessible ONLY to authorised users through a secured VPN or VDI access?','IRDAI CSF Compliance','technical','detective','annual',TRUE),
