(NULL,'IRDAI.IGDM.335','Has the intermediary prominently published on its website, mobile based application or both, as the case may be, the rul','Has the intermediary prominently published on its website, mobile based application or both, as the case may be, the rules and regulations, privacy policy and user agreement for access or usage of its computer resource by any person?','IRDAI CSF Compliance','technical','detective','annual',TRUE),
(NULL,'IRDAI.IGDM.336','Has the rules and regulations, privacy policy or user agreement of the intermediary informed the user of its computer re','Has the rules and regulations, privacy policy or user agreement of the intermediary informed the user of its computer resource not to host, display, upload, modify, publish, transmit, store, update or share any information that (i) belongs to another person and to which the user does not have any right; (ii) is defamatory, obscene, pornographic, paedopholic, invasive of another privacy including bodily privacy, insulting or harassing on the basis of gender, libellous, racially or ethnically obje','IRDAI CSF Compliance','technical','detective','annual',TRUE),
(NULL,'IRDAI.IGDM.337','Has the intermediary periodically informed its users, at least once every year, that in case of non- compliance with rul','Has the intermediary periodically informed its users, at least once every year, that in case of non- compliance with rules and regulations, privacy policy or user agreement for access or usage of the computer resource of such intermediary, it has the right to terminate the access or usage rights of the users to the computer resource immediately or remove non-compliant information or both, as the case may be','IRDAI CSF Compliance','technical','detective','annual',TRUE),
(NULL,'IRDAI.IGDM.338','Has the intermediary, on whose computer resource the information is stored, hosted or published, upon receiving actual k','Has the intermediary, on whose computer resource the information is stored, hosted or published, upon receiving actual knowledge in the form of an order by a court of competent jurisdiction or on being notified by the Appropriate Government or its agency under clause (b) of sub-section (3) of section 79 of the Act, not host, store or publish any unlawful information, which is prohibited under any law for the time being in force relation to the interest of the sovereignty and','IRDAI CSF Compliance','technical','detective','annual',TRUE),
(NULL,'IRDAI.IGDM.339','Has the intermediary periodically, and at least once in a year, informed its users of its rules and regulations, privacy','Has the intermediary periodically, and at least once in a year, informed its users of its rules and regulations, privacy policy or user agreement or any change in the  rules and regulations, privacy policy or user agreement, as the case may be','IRDAI CSF Compliance','technical','detective','annual',TRUE),
(NULL,'IRDAI.IGDM.340','If the intermediary collected information from a user for registration on the computer resource, has it retained his inf','If the intermediary collected information from a user for registration on the computer resource, has it retained his information for a period of one hundred and eighty days after any cancellation or withdrawal of his registration, as the case maybe','IRDAI CSF Compliance','technical','detective','annual',TRUE),
(NULL,'IRDAI.IGDM.341','Has the intermediary taken all reasonable measures to secure its computer resource and information contained therein fol','Has the intermediary taken all reasonable measures to secure its computer resource and information contained therein following the reasonable security practices and procedures as prescribed in the Information Technology (Reasonable Security Practices and Procedures and Sensitive Personal Information) Rules, 2011','IRDAI CSF Compliance','technical','detective','annual',TRUE),
(NULL,'IRDAI.IGDM.342','Does the intermediary, as soon as possible, but not later than seventy two hours of the receipt of an order, provide inf','Does the intermediary, as soon as possible, but not later than seventy two hours of the receipt of an order, provide information under its control or possession, or assistance to Government agency which is lawfully authorised for investigative or protective or cyber security activities, for the purposes of verification of identity, or for the prevention, detection, investigation, or prosecution, of offences under any law for the time being in force, or for cyber security incidents','IRDAI CSF Compliance','technical','detective','annual',TRUE),
(NULL,'IRDAI.IGDM.343','Has the intermediary reported cyber security incidents and share related information with the Indian Computer Emergency ','Has the intermediary reported cyber security incidents and share related information with the Indian Computer Emergency Response Team in accordance with the policies and procedures as mentioned in the Information Technology (The Indian Computer Emergency Response Team and Manner of Performing Functions and Duties) Rules, 2013.','IRDAI CSF Compliance','technical','detective','annual',TRUE),
(NULL,'IRDAI.IGDM.344','Is the intermediary aware that it shall not knowingly deploy or install or modify technical configuration of computer re','Is the intermediary aware that it shall not knowingly deploy or install or modify technical configuration of computer resource or become party to any act that may change or has the potential to change the normal course of operation of the computer resource than what it is supposed to perform thereby circumventing any law for the time being in force','IRDAI CSF Compliance','technical','detective','annual',TRUE),
