(NULL,'IRDAI.IGDM.346','Has the intermediary, within twenty-four hours from the receipt of a complaint made by an individual or any person on hi','Has the intermediary, within twenty-four hours from the receipt of a complaint made by an individual or any person on his behalf under this sub-rule, in relation to any content which is prima facie in the nature of any material which exposes the private area of such individual, shows such individual in full or partial nudity or shows or depicts such individual in any sexual act or conduct, or is in the nature of impersonation in an electronic form, including artificially morphed images of such i','IRDAI CSF Compliance','technical','detective','annual',TRUE),
(NULL,'IRDAI.IGDM.347','Has the intermediary implemented a mechanism for the receipt of complaints under clause (b) of this sub-rule which may e','Has the intermediary implemented a mechanism for the receipt of complaints under clause (b) of this sub-rule which may enable the individual or person to provide details, as may be necessary, in relation to such content or communication link','IRDAI CSF Compliance','technical','detective','annual',TRUE)
